V2 hardware:
pi zero
modem - ozzmaker SARA-R5
GPS - ozzmaker SARA-R5
IMU - ozzmaker SARA-R5 on i2c


Startup working script:
sara_r5_startup.sh

precondition: installation of Multiplexing gsmMuxd from ozzmaker git according to ozzmaker manual:
https://ozzmaker.com/how-to-enable-multiplexing-on-the-raspberry-pi-serial-interface/

the script should be run from crontab:
by adding:
@reboot /home/proscout/sara_r5_startup.sh